      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BRINDLE SURPRISE (8) flew the lids with a fast early split last time, hitting the frame with a 0.8 lengths second (34.75) over 600m at this track and making it two placings on end. Didn't win last time but still ran one of the quickest times on the card. Well-placed to take this out. BANDIT DARYL (4) has been beaten for early speed lately, last time finishing fourth (34.59) in a Restricted WIN at this track. Form at the trip sound including four wins. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Key player if finds best. EDWARD NIGMA (5) has been hard to follow lately, running fourth (34.75) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Key player on best and worth another try. POCKET RIOT (1) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can bounce back.",
